        "timestamp": "2019-01-29 16:29:07.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nThere are several reviews submitted for this JIRA, Jorge can you please inspect whether this align's with our Dublin goals? Thanks.\n\nKryzsztof, can you let us know what your company is working on? And why you need these changes?",
