          "username": "jhh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-01-29 17:09:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nKrzysztof has my agreement on reworking the Topic Factories for UEB and DMaaP, the work was proposed under POLICY-1387 and POLICY-1486 that this review points at is a subtask.   See comments in POLICY-1387.  I agree that there's a lot of copy/pasted code there, especially the DMaaP* classes that pretty much were duplicated from the UEB ones.   It should help at least with the sonar metrics with regards to code duplication.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
